These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, water, coffee
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, game, aristoff
City: edinburgh, liverpool, miami
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, scientist, teacher
1. the person drinking water is between the prince-smoker and the accountant##2
2. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
3. the scientist is on the right of the accountant##1
4. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the game-smoker##1
5. the person drinking water is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
6. the prince-smoker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |     3      |
| Beverage          | mirinda      | water        | coffee     |
| Cigar         | aristoff | game | prince    |
| City   | liverpool   | edinburgh       | miami |
| Job         | accountant  | scientist      | teacher    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, tea, 7up
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, january, june
There 3 different types of food: strawberry, cherry, papaya
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: dahlia, begonia, zinnia
1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
2. the person who's birthday is in january is the person drinking tea##1
3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
4. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person eating cherry##1
5. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
6. the person drinking 7up is in an even position##4
7. the person who growszinnia is between the person who's birthday is in january and the person drinking juice##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3      |
| Beverage           | tea    | 7up | juice |
| Birthday   | january | july       | june   |
| Food           | papaya  | cherry   | strawberry     |
| Flower         | begonia | zinnia       | dahlia   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: woodworking, hiking, photography
The people have 3 different jobs:  security-guard, architect, manager
There are 3 different nationalities: indonesian, egyptian, russian
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, house, indie
1. the russian is on the right of the fan of classical##1
2. the person who's hobby is photography is the fan of indie##1
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is between the architect and the fan of indie##2
5. the security-guard is in an even position##4
6. the russian is the person who's hobby is hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3     |
| Hobby          | photography | woodworking | hiking |
| Job   | manager     | security-guard | architect |
| Nationality           | egyptian       | indonesian   | russian    |
| Music-Genre     | indie      | classical   | house |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-4::.
City: colone, venice, new-york
House: colonial, cape-cod, ranch-style
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: hip-hop, trance, funk
3 different games are played: scrabble, mah-jongg, domino
1. the person traveling to colone is on the left or right of the fan of trance##3
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
3. the ranch-style house is the fan of trance##1
4. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far right##1
5. the colonial house is on the right of the person playing domino##1
6. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing domino##1
7. the person traveling to new-york is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |      3      |
| City         | venice  | colone       | new-york |
| House           | ranch-style     | cape-cod      | colonial   |
| Music-Genre   | trance | hip-hop | funk     |
| Game   | scrabble      | domino   | mah-jongg     |

