.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-5::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: turquise, ivory, purple
The people have 3 different hobbies: woodworking, board-games, drawing
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: volleyball, weightlifting, cricket
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, sunflower, iris
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
2. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
6. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who likes ivory##1
7. the person who growsiris is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3        |
| Color      | purple     | ivory   | turquise         |
| Hobby           | woodworking | board-games | drawing |
| Sport   | cricket      | weightlifting   | volleyball            |
| Flower   | sunflower   | iris  | amaryllis         |

