.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-6::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: traveling, dancing, singing
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, subway, helicopter
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, october, may
There are 3 different favourite colors: pink, lilac, red
1. the person who's birthday is in october is between the person driving the subway and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
2. the person who likes pink is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is the person who likes lilac##1
4. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the person who likes pink is in an even position##4
6. the person who likes pink is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |      3      |
| Hobby          | singing    | traveling     | dancing |
| Transport           | subway | helicopter | car      |
| Birthday   | may      | october       | january    |
| Color   | lilac      | pink         | red     |

