.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-7::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: traveling, magic-tricks, hiking
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: water-polo, swimming, cricket
3 different games are played: whist, poker, scrabble
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: bellflower, amaryllis, balloon-flower
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is in the middle##1
2. the person playing poker is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
3. the person who's sport is cricket is the person who growsamaryllis##1
4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left or right of the person who's sport is water-polo##3
5. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
6. the person playing whist is between the person who growsamaryllis and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##2
7. the person who growsballoon-flower is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Hobby          | magic-tricks | traveling | hiking |
| Sport   | swimming  | water-polo    | cricket |
| Game   | poker  | whist   | scrabble    |
| Flower     | balloon-flower   | bellflower       | amaryllis |

