3. the townhouse house is in an odd position##4
4. the person who growslily is on the left of the journalist##1
5. the person who growslily is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
6. the person who growstulip is in an odd position##4
7. the photographer is between the vegafina-smoker and the person who growsbellflower##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |
| House      | townhouse | gothic-revival    | tower  |
| Job         | designer        | photographer   | journalist   |
| Cigar   | cain       | dannemann    | vegafina |
| Flower     | bellflower          | lily | tulip       |

