.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-10::.
3 different games are played: domino, chess, mah-jongg
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, almond-milk, iced-tea
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, june, october
House: craftsman, cottage, farmhouse
1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the craftsman house##1
2. the person drinking water is the person playing domino##1
3. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the person drinking water is the person who's birthday is in october##1
5. the cottage house is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
6. the person playing domino is in an odd position##4
7. the person playing domino is on the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |
| Game           | domino     | mah-jongg    | chess |
| Beverage   | water  | almond-milk | iced-tea      |
| Birthday   | october       | june   | march    |
| House     | cottage | farmhouse        | craftsman     |

