.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-11::.
3 different games are played: chess, backgammon, scrabble
There are 3 different favourite colors: brown, azure, green
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: soul, d&b, hip-hop
The people use 3 different means of transport: taxi, car, airplane
1. the person who likes azure is in an odd position##4
2. the person who likes azure is the fan of soul##1
3. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
4. the person playing scrabble is in an odd position##4
5. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
6. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
7. the person who likes green is the fan of hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |      3       |
| Game      | scrabble     | backgammon      | chess  |
| Color          | azure     | green | brown       |
| Music-Genre   | soul  | hip-hop    | d&b      |
| Transport         | airplane | taxi  | car |

