3. the person who likes apricot is on the far right##1
4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person who growsdaisy##3
5. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
6. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is between the person who's hobby is fishing and the person who likes red##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Hobby      | video-games       | magic-tricks   | fishing |
| Birthday   | july | may     | january |
| Color           | red      | turquise | apricot    |
| Flower         | balloon-flower  | zinnia     | daisy |

