City: nizza, rome, paris
1. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the oliveros-smoker##3
2. the blend-smoker is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1
3. the oliveros-smoker is in an even position##4
4. the person eating cucumber is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking cola is the person traveling to paris##1
6. the person eating cranberry is in the middle##1
7. the person traveling to rome is on the far left##1
8. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
9. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| Cigar           | blend | oliveros   | pall-mall |
| Food   | broccoli  | cranberry    | cucumber    |
| Beverage         | tea    | cola | juice   |
| City     | rome  | paris     | nizza  |

