4. the social-worker is the person who's hobby is writing##1
5. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far right##1
6. the fan of d&b is on the right of the librarian##1
7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is photography##3
8. the social-worker is on the left of the fan of house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |     3      |
| Beverage          | water     | almond-milk   | iced-tea     |
