The people prefer 3 different types of sport: water-polo, biathlon, swimming
House: cape-cod, futuristic, wooden
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, july, april
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is in an even position##4
2. the person who growsballoon-flower is between the person who growstulip and the person who's birthday is in april##2
3. the cape-cod house is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
4. the person who growsdaisy is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
6. the person who growsdaisy is on the left or right of the futuristic house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |
| Flower          | daisy     | balloon-flower | tulip   |
| Sport         | swimming   | water-polo | biathlon |
| House   | wooden | futuristic       | cape-cod   |
| Birthday     | april     | may  | july        |

