2. the person who growsrose is between the person who growsdahlia and the person who likes emerald##2
3. the person who's sport is tennis is the modern house##1
4. the futuristic house is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
5. the person who likes blue is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's sport is baseball is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2        |     3      |
| Sport      | tennis         | water-polo         | baseball       |
| Color         | blue          | ebony        | emerald |
| Flower           | dahlia | rose | azalea     |
| House   | modern      | futuristic          | gothic-revival     |

