.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-19::.
City: marseilles, venice, prague
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: mystery, satire, thriller
3 different pets are kept: mouse, pony, hamster
The people have 3 different jobs:  freelancer, musician, doctor
1. the musician is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the person watching thriller movies##3
3. the musician is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
4. the doctor is the person traveling to prague##1
5. the owner of the hamster is in an even position##4
6. the person watching mystery movies is the owner of the pony##1
7. the owner of the mouse is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person traveling to venice is the person watching satire movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3    |
| City          | venice  | marseilles   | prague |
| Movie-Genre   | satire      | thriller      | mystery   |
| Pet   | mouse     | hamster | pony |
| Job         | musician | freelancer   | doctor   |

