4. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
5. the havana-smoker is on the left or right of the bolivar-smoker##3
6. the havana-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2        |     3      |
| Cigar           | bolivar  | havana | bongani   |
| Sport   | basketball | skiing           | swimming      |
| Flower           | amaryllis   | aconite          | poppy |
| Game     | bridge    | whist           | mah-jongg |

 